WEBVTT

00:00.681 --> 00:02.415
Who will rule once I am gone?

00:04.205 --> 00:06.173
- The king is dead.
- Long live the king.

00:06.174 --> 00:09.376
- This is...
- That's Jack. Jack's a bastard.

00:09.377 --> 00:10.777
He's a gifted bastard.

00:10.778 --> 00:13.447
The way to my daughter's heart
is through affection.

00:14.682 --> 00:17.250
Bartholomew has sided
against King Stephen.

00:17.251 --> 00:18.785
He's turned traitor.

00:18.786 --> 00:21.355
- You're under attack!
- We must defend the king!

00:22.390 --> 00:25.525
- Halt!
- Thank you, Earl of Shiring.

00:25.526 --> 00:27.627
- My name is Ellen.
- Tom.

00:27.628 --> 00:29.062
Tom the builder.

00:29.063 --> 00:32.499
Why can't God give me work
just this once?

00:32.500 --> 00:34.368
What happened?

00:34.369 --> 00:35.635
We can stay now.

00:37.672 --> 00:40.707
<i>You can't rebuild
a cathedral without its relic.</i>

00:40.708 --> 00:42.609
<i>This may be
the devil's work</i>

00:42.610 --> 00:45.112
<i>but it was God that
sent you a master builder.</i>

00:45.113 --> 00:47.481
What makes you think
there'll be a new church?

00:47.482 --> 00:49.816
- I will build it.
- I swear by all that's holy,

00:49.817 --> 00:51.351
you'll never build your church.

00:51.352 --> 00:53.086
- Aaah!
- No!

00:55.957 --> 00:59.426
Richard, listen to me.
You mustn't tell anyone, ever.

01:00.528 --> 01:02.829
Piss on you, Lord Bishop.

01:04.031 --> 01:06.233
We've begun.

01:06.234 --> 01:16.234
